{"title":"挑水的女子","authors":["耿翔"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水的女子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗亮高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是沉静了一夜的水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘过山尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片头巾，为大地抹出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水的女子，我听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们被水声碰响的手镯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土坡上，有许多情歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就埋在盛水的木桶里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今早的露珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬上豌豆细嫩的秧子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多像一对亮眼眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把高原看得透彻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水的女子，踩一组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开翅膀的舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我闻见东方的花香里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮满你们的笑声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再陡的高坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也被一根桑木扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪出冷汗。那些把你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执著放在心上的人呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就守在水边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今早，我最好的感觉是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和忙碌着的你们擦肩而过"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}